Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.16,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜避難之處被地機所波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而這並不是波蕾的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論任何時代...\n小孩也是戰爭的受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十九話 露的逃亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.75,0:02:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了尋找哈曼艦隊\n雅加瑪急速啟航了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.76,0:02:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此高達沒搜尋莉娜就離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還以為不用穿太空衣\n但竟然這麼大風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好讓你清醒點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.39,0:02:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人太清醒,連哈欠也打不出\n臭捷度,讓我增加無謂的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度還沒從終端機出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,亞蘭特出去將他運回來了\n身特拉穆艦方面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:03:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒任何資料送來\n真慢,再幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.27,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,膝蓋關節僵硬,幫我檢查看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不夠潤滑油吧\n是因為內部進了沙粒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.16,0:03:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麻煩了\n唯有先拆開用油清洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,捷度在哪裏?\n還有一各駕駛員沒出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合體部的亞蘭特去看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.12,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那捷度呢?\n正被回收吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擊太大不行了嗎\n別胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.70,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是MS的駕駛員\n只為了妹妹的生死而一振不起的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.19,0:03:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不能去戰鬥吧\n這種聽厭的話別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.93,0:03:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達已全部收回,可能關閉機艙\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度感覺不到莉娜的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他是新人類,明確感覺到妹妹死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潔度可以感覺到\n遠離他的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是人類本身的第六感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只因為太依賴科學而失去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白,明白\n但捷度還不是完全的新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只不過太感情用事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏?\n我要讓捷度清醒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你隨著他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.28,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也會有想一人獨處的時候\n你隨著他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.75,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,因為潤滑油快用完了\n你用花事寧代替吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.89,0:04:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說笑了,那是MS,出了意外怎麼辦\n等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎,那兩個人真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.38,0:04:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...打開機蓋吧\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.57,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,等捷度他自己出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓他頹廢到何時?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們需要一起戰鬥的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.77,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,捷度很可憐\n誰也不能干擾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開,波蕾\n不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為捷度好\n就照我的話做,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!你真過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.07,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度出來吧,快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你是這種男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.94,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後有更多的無辜者慘死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾千萬人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為命令而無端的被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而行兇者就是駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟捷度無關\n有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是戰爭\n戰爭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.06,0:06:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,這就是戰爭\n不憤的話就再次喚回作戰之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,莉娜她死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.43,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別管我啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.18,0:06:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這縮頭烏龜\n哭哭啼啼到何時?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別得寸進尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快抓住捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.51,0:06:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,現在你不知會有何行動\n冷靜一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加拉帕和亞加瑪將會合\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.18,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使不增強但數量增加\n對我們也構成威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來,那女孩怎樣了?叫莉娜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.62,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真的是你心裏話嗎?\n我不明白你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼年輕就如此冷酷\n我只是實話實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.20,0:07:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看那所謂的真實\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.71,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去鎮壓北邊殘餘之眾,你去對付加拉帕\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.04,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘了我們都擁有沙比家的血統\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別阻礙我們,波蕾\n我叫你們放手 很痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度很慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.62,0:07:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該溫柔點\n放開她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,但是...\n不要緊,放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?捷度\n走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.11,0:08:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不明白我的心情\n我明白捷度的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.56,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是莉娜\n所以不可能取代莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.53,0:08:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但今天起我會成為你的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.14,0:08:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果我不是波蕾呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.44,0:08:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想加拉帕\n會在艾雷亞迎擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.86,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那裏有飛機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可能是他們的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.66,0:08:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吩咐德萊森部隊進攻艾雷亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我隨後就到\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.27,0:09:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜的確不在了\n果然是亞羅娜帶她一起死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又再講無聊的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為所愛的人而死真愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況是單戀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.31,0:09:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但正是因為如此才更可怕嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人身邊的\n都是唯利是圖之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德萊森部隊現在出擊\n作戰計劃如剛才說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各隊員上機出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AMX-009出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.49,0:09:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧古斯你想監視我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.16,0:09:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看見剛才露卡的態度嗎?\n嗯...太強硬了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,可以拿那個給我嗎?\n比查,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接住吧\n麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你是故意的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.08,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦...去看看膝部關節修理好了沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.79,0:10:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等等\n比查,她來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是什麼意思?\n想要抓弄人也要有點分寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你太輕視別人的哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指捷度的事?\n哼,那慘不忍睹的出場樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白什麼?\n我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了\n反正你又不是來自報廢鐵廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度能生存至今\n是因為他是新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.93,0:10:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏\n讓有能力的新人類成長,對聯邦軍也是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.95,0:10:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事和我們無關\n你是聯邦均的走狗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.18,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直是小孩子的吵架\n你說什麼?可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.69,0:11:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹什麼\n你這女人真暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莫迪先出手的\n受傷該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你希望的話就如你所願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,當波蕾是俘虜是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長,有緊急通訊\n是從艾雷亞來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.49,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾雷亞受到辛吉翁軍所襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪及MS隊快前去救援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.91,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改變方向,各船員各就各位\n是  傳令各船員就位...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.81,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有分寸點阿\n自以為自己是正規軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直裝作是旁觀者阿\n叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.93,0:11:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想臨陣退縮嗎?\n想臨陣退縮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡想用核戰機逃跑\n你們有分寸點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,露卡好像逃跑了\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何擅自外出\n露卡,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查.奧雷格以百式出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉.比安諾以Z高達出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪.阿卡爾以MK2出動\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.你出擊沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算困在房裏也不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛?那加油阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,我也乘核戰機出動\n那拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.75,0:13:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度提起精神\n沒精神的捷度不是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.50,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不認為戰爭能打起精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但或許露卡所說是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發了,伊萊!\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.86,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒精神的捷度不是捷度\n對阿,波蕾,我也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.05,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾雷亞在這方向嗎?\n這簡直是標明記號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是城市?\n艾雷亞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她想飛往巖堆躲藏\n我們夾攻她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.98,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然出現了這麼強的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲在雲層比較有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍嗎?\n這裏交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.68,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去攻打艾雷亞\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然逃走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.34,0:14:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,偵查機飛往你那邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?\n那是古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,好機會\n用核戰機做盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用核戰機做盾牌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明不是迷戀著露卡嗎?\n對阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開典\n找我做盾牌連你也會沒命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我另有計劃\n露卡你來我前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只對你們有好處吧?\n不是阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有點異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為了對付有偵察裝置的戰機\n最好的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只顧著逃,遲早被擊落哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.19,0:15:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查\n我一定為你擊敗他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,艾莉,為我掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打算做什麼?\n你聽到嗎?她是露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰鬥機內的是露卡,仔細看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是露卡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想逃嗎\n比查,別再胡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做個有用的盾牌,好好擋著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.46,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有種就射吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.57,0:16:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿,透過這核戰機攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要跟你一起瘋了\n果然是露卡,露卡,我是古利明.托托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.85,0:17:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真凄慘..比查那傢伙給我記著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明說要捨棄自我,但又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.24,0:17:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明為了那女人露出破綻\n真是自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,是男人擅自露出破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達隊回答\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.82,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?快去艾雷亞\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來遲了嗎?\n看來是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.22,0:18:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟將所有人捲入戰場,我不管是吉翁\n或是新吉翁也好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度?好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.30,0:18:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點,捷度,雖然我不既為戰爭能提起精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但露卡也提醒了我們重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.67,0:18:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎?以後有更多的無辜者慘死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.24,0:18:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不憤的話就再次喚回作戰之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,我們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會放過你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊比較有利...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,這個交給我吧\n不好意思,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到反擊這麼迅速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.15,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是剛才的傢伙嗎?古利明真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.51,0:19:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各隊員,行動目的已達到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退出艾雷亞,作戰成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃了嗎?\n別追了,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先為城市撲火吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧古斯那個臭傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達部隊回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那露卡的核戰機呢?\n還沒..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡離開了亞加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.56,0:21:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡無所謂,重要的是核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.05,0:21:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種說法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.59,0:21:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不抑制個人情緒會害死大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.00,0:21:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡違抗命令\n還濫用亞加瑪的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罪不可恕\n那是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.85,0:21:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家辛苦了,快去休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宣斯朗,拿得到艾雷亞的訊號嗎?\n還沒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.36,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.47,0:21:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管露卡了\n對,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非你們對露卡怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阿,比查和莫迪他們\n伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.73,0:21:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我和莉娜的是責怪了露卡嗎?\n嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.63,0:21:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是因為我哭哭啼啼的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡她心灰意冷要離開了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.19,0:22:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機..\n莫非在那的是露卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.23,0:22:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從悲傷中得不到任何東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.05,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥吧,捷度\n那才是生存之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.49,0:22:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別敗於悲傷中,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.94,0:23:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露和古利明在沙漠的小鎮裏迷了路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.86,0:23:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏有背負著深厚的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.22,0:23:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並討厭去宇宙的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.45,0:24:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 兩人之間有處於敵我雙方這一悲傷的隔閡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.76,0:24:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 藍色部隊 前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.77,0:24:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠裏吹起了藍色的風

